snippet.textDisplay:
“Pop smoke,” the character is dead. The actual “rapper,” guy is alive. He was auctioning off his appearance on Asian media lmao when I was in Asia it aired. It also showed on YouTube for a little before it got removed. I swear on everything I love... i would release the footages I have but he went as far as having a funeral!!!’ It opened my eyes so much how powerful a PR team is in hiding things bc I can’t really find it on the surface .. so I really don’t want to ruin guys career officially since he obviously made a decision on killing his character off. I know you won’t believe me but they went as far as holding the funeral for a reason so I am going to let you guys believe me or not for now. Bc I know FOR A FACT he’s alive I saw with my own eyes man crazy and have a clip of him literally auctioning coming out on Asian media.... shows you this music industry and just media alone!! I’ll tell you this when he came out auctioning himself it was his manager there first then pop smoke came out and they offered $250k!!!!hahahahhaa QUOTE “we didn’t really think through,” so I guarantee if you spread that quote and if “pop smoke,” sees it he knows he can be exposed. Happy dude didn’t really die but I guess rip “pop smoke,” the character.

I don’t ever disrespect the dead so please don’t accuse me of conspiracies lol i has video clips . If you got that quote to him and situation I explained I guarantee he’s gna sweat but I’ll let the guy be for now..... it’s just not right playing with death you dig!!!? That’s what’s having me sit on it bc like I want him to eat he came from the hood... hopefully he eventually comes out when he finishes making all his money. Because I may just leak it , but I’ll let him eat for now so believe me or not but I swear on my Moms my story is real.
